snippet.title: Amicade - PC Gameplay (Steam)
snippet.description:
Amicade is a nostalgic trip to the arcades, where you'll find three Score Attack games with online Leaderboards - all set to Free Play!

These games were originally made within 24 hours each, using various assets for graphics and sound, then later combined into this arcade collection. As a big fan of classic games from the Atari to the Amiga, this was a ton of fun for the developer to make!

Amicade (C) Gaterooze, Ink
Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2457970/Amicade/
